**Summary**:

| What you want to do | Allowed? |
|---|---|
| Read the docs for learning | ✅ Yes |
| Run the code locally for personal research / audit | ✅ Yes |
| Fork on GitHub and improve under the same licenses | ✅ Yes |
| Run an internal scraper at your company that uses this code | ⚠️ Yes, but the modified source must be available to your internal users (AGPL-3.0 §13) |
| Wrap the code into a commercial SaaS / paid product | ❌ Must open-source the entire stack under AGPL-3.0 |
| Sell access to documentation / republish for profit | ❌ CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 forbids commercial use |
| Use the methodology to train a commercial AI model | ❌ Commercial use of CC-NC content not allowed |
| Cite in an academic paper | ✅ Yes (see README §17 BibTeX) |

For questions or licensing requests beyond these tracks, open a GitHub Issue.
